#. class="division">
msgctxt "dn11:1.1"
msgid "Dīgha Nikāya 11"
msgstr "Long Discourses 11"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "dn11:2.1"
msgid "Kevaṭṭasutta"
msgstr "With Kevaddha"

#. </h1></div><p><a class="sc" id="1"></a><a class="wp" id="wp1"></a><a
#. class="pts" id="pts1.211"></a>
msgctxt "dn11:3.1"
msgid "<span class=\"evam\">Evaṃ me sutaṃ—​</span>"
msgstr "<span class=”evam”>​So I have heard.</span>"

msgctxt "dn11:3.2"
msgid "ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā nāḷandāyaṃ viharati pāvārikambavane."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was staying near Nālandā in Pāvārika’s mango grove. "

msgctxt "dn11:3.3"
msgid "Atha kho kevaṭṭo gahapatiputto yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami;"
msgstr "Then the householder Kevaddha went up to the Buddha,"

msgctxt "dn11:3.4"
msgid "upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi."
msgstr "bowed, sat down to one side, "

msgctxt "dn11:3.5"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho kevaṭṭo gahapatiputto bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "and said to him:"

msgctxt "dn11:3.6"
msgid ""
"“ayaṃ, bhante, nāḷandā iddhā ceva phītā ca bahujanā ākiṇṇamanussā bhagavati "
"abhippasannā."
msgstr "“Sir, this Nāḷanda is successful and prosperous and full of people."

msgctxt "dn11:3.7"
msgid ""
"Sādhu, bhante, bhagavā ekaṃ bhikkhuṃ samādisatu, yo uttari manussadhammā "
"iddhipāṭihāriyaṃ karissati;"
msgstr ""
"Sir, please direct a mendicant to perform a demonstration of superhuman "
"psychic power."

msgctxt "dn11:3.8"
msgid "evāyaṃ nāḷandā bhiyyoso mattāya bhagavati abhippasīdissatī”ti."
msgstr "Then Nāḷandā will become even more devoted to the Buddha!”"

msgctxt "dn11:3.9"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, bhagavā kevaṭṭaṃ gahapatiputtaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "When he said this, The Buddha said:"

msgctxt "dn11:3.10"
msgid "“na kho ahaṃ, kevaṭṭa, bhikkhūnaṃ evaṃ dhammaṃ desemi:"
msgstr "“Kevaddha, I do not teach the mendicants like this:"

msgctxt "dn11:3.11"
msgid ""
"‘etha tumhe, bhikkhave, gihīnaṃ odātavasanānaṃ uttari manussadhammā "
"iddhipāṭihāriyaṃ karothā’”ti."
msgstr ""
"‘Come now, mendicants, perform a demonstration of superhuman psychic power "
"for the white-clothed laypeople.’”"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="2"></a><a class="wp" id="wp2"></a><a class="pts"
#. id="pts1.212"></a>
msgctxt "dn11:4.1"
msgid "Dutiyampi kho kevaṭṭo gahapatiputto bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "For a second time, Kevaddha made the same request, "

msgctxt "dn11:4.2"
msgid "“nāhaṃ, bhante, bhagavantaṃ dhaṃsemi;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn11:4.3"
msgid "api ca evaṃ vadāmi:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn11:4.4"
msgid ""
"‘ayaṃ, bhante, nāḷandā iddhā ceva phītā ca bahujanā ākiṇṇamanussā bhagavati "
"abhippasannā."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn11:4.5"
msgid ""
"Sādhu, bhante, bhagavā ekaṃ bhikkhuṃ samādisatu, yo uttari manussadhammā "
"iddhipāṭihāriyaṃ karissati;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn11:4.6"
msgid "evāyaṃ nāḷandā bhiyyoso mattāya bhagavati abhippasīdissatī’”ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn11:4.7"
msgid "Dutiyampi kho bhagavā kevaṭṭaṃ gahapatiputtaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "and the Buddha gave the same answer."

msgctxt "dn11:4.8"
msgid "“na kho ahaṃ, kevaṭṭa, bhikkhūnaṃ evaṃ dhammaṃ desemi:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn11:4.9"
msgid ""
"‘etha tumhe, bhikkhave, gihīnaṃ odātavasanānaṃ uttari manussadhammā "
"iddhipāṭihāriyaṃ karothā’”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="3"></a><a class="wp" id="wp3"></a>
msgctxt "dn11:5.1"
msgid "Tatiyampi kho kevaṭṭo gahapatiputto bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "For a third time, Kevaddha made the same request, "

msgctxt "dn11:5.2"
msgid "“nāhaṃ, bhante, bhagavantaṃ dhaṃsemi;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn11:5.3"
msgid "api ca evaṃ vadāmi:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn11:5.4"
msgid ""
"‘ayaṃ, bhante, nāḷandā iddhā ceva phītā ca bahujanā ākiṇṇamanussā bhagavati "
"abhippasannā."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn11:5.5"
msgid ""
"Sādhu, bhante, bhagavā ekaṃ bhikkhuṃ samādisatu, yo uttari manussadhammā "
"iddhipāṭihāriyaṃ karissati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn11:5.6"
msgid "Evāyaṃ nāḷandā bhiyyoso mattāya bhagavati abhippasīdissatī’”ti."
msgstr "and the Buddha said this:"

#. </p><h2>
msgctxt "dn11:6.1"
msgid "1. Iddhipāṭihāriya"
msgstr "Demonstrations of Psychic Power"

#. </h2><p><a class="sc" id="4"></a>
msgctxt "dn11:7.1"
msgid ""
"“Tīṇi kho imāni, kevaṭṭa, pāṭihāriyāni mayā sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā "
"paveditāni."
msgstr ""
"“Kevaddha, there are three kinds of demonstration, which I declare having "
"realized them with my own insight."

msgctxt "dn11:7.2"
msgid "Katamāni tīṇi?"
msgstr "What three?"

msgctxt "dn11:7.3"
msgid "Iddhipāṭihāriyaṃ, ādesanāpāṭihāriyaṃ, anusāsanīpāṭihāriyaṃ."
msgstr ""
"A demonstration of psychic power, a demonstration of revealing, and a "
"demonstration of instruction."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="5"></a><a class="wp" id="wp4"></a>
msgctxt "dn11:8.1"
msgid "Katamañca, kevaṭṭa, iddhipāṭihāriyaṃ?"
msgstr "And what is the demonstration of psychic power?"

msgctxt "dn11:8.2"
msgid "Idha, kevaṭṭa, bhikkhu anekavihitaṃ iddhividhaṃ paccanubhoti—"
msgstr "It’s a mendicant who wields the many kinds of psychic power:"

msgctxt "dn11:8.3"
msgid "ekopi hutvā bahudhā hoti, bahudhāpi hutvā eko hoti;"
msgstr "multiplying themselves and becoming one again; "

msgctxt "dn11:8.4"
msgid ""
"āvibhāvaṃ tirobhāvaṃ tirokuṭṭaṃ tiropākāraṃ tiropabbataṃ asajjamāno gacchati "
"seyyathāpi ākāse;"
msgstr ""
"going unimpeded through a wall, a rampart, or a mountain as if through space;"
" "

msgctxt "dn11:8.5"
msgid "pathaviyāpi ummujjanimujjaṃ karoti seyyathāpi udake;"
msgstr "diving in and out of the earth as if it was water; "

msgctxt "dn11:8.6"
msgid "udakepi abhijjamāne gacchati seyyathāpi pathaviyaṃ;"
msgstr "walking on water as if it was earth; "

msgctxt "dn11:8.7"
msgid "ākāsepi pallaṅkena kamati seyyathāpi pakkhī sakuṇo;"
msgstr "flying cross-legged through the air like a bird;"

msgctxt "dn11:8.8"
msgid ""
"imepi candimasūriye evaṃ mahiddhike evaṃ mahānubhāve pāṇinā parāmasati "
"parimajjati;"
msgstr ""
"touching and stroking with the hand the sun and moon, so mighty and powerful;"

msgctxt "dn11:8.9"
msgid "yāva brahmalokāpi kāyena vasaṃ vatteti."
msgstr "controlling the body as far as the Brahmā realm. "

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="6"></a><a class="pts" id="pts1.213"></a>
msgctxt "dn11:9.1"
msgid ""
"Tamenaṃ aññataro saddho pasanno passati taṃ bhikkhuṃ anekavihitaṃ "
"iddhividhaṃ paccanubhontaṃ—"
msgstr ""
"Then someone with faith and confidence sees that mendicant performing those "
"superhuman feats."

msgctxt "dn11:9.2"
msgid "ekopi hutvā bahudhā hontaṃ, bahudhāpi hutvā eko hontaṃ;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn11:9.3"
msgid "āvibhāvaṃ tirobhāvaṃ;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn11:9.4"
msgid ""
"tirokuṭṭaṃ tiropākāraṃ tiropabbataṃ asajjamānaṃ gacchantaṃ seyyathāpi ākāse;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn11:9.5"
msgid "pathaviyāpi ummujjanimujjaṃ karontaṃ seyyathāpi udake;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn11:9.6"
msgid "udakepi abhijjamāne gacchantaṃ seyyathāpi pathaviyaṃ;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn11:9.7"
msgid "ākāsepi pallaṅkena kamantaṃ seyyathāpi pakkhī sakuṇo;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn11:9.8"
msgid ""
"imepi candimasūriye evaṃ mahiddhike evaṃ mahānubhāve pāṇinā parāmasantaṃ "
"parimajjantaṃ yāva brahmalokāpi kāyena vasaṃ vattentaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="7"></a>
msgctxt "dn11:10.1"
msgid "Tamenaṃ so saddho pasanno aññatarassa assaddhassa appasannassa āroceti:"
msgstr "They tell someone else who lacks faith and confidence:"

msgctxt "dn11:10.2"
msgid ""
"‘acchariyaṃ vata bho, abbhutaṃ vata bho, samaṇassa mahiddhikatā "
"mahānubhāvatā."
msgstr ""
"‘It’s incredible, it’s amazing! The ascetic has such psychic power and might!"

msgctxt "dn11:10.3"
msgid "Amāhaṃ bhikkhuṃ addasaṃ anekavihitaṃ iddhividhaṃ paccanubhontaṃ—"
msgstr "I saw him myself, performing all these superhuman feats!’"

msgctxt "dn11:10.4"
msgid "ekopi hutvā bahudhā hontaṃ, bahudhāpi hutvā eko hontaṃ …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn11:10.5"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn11:10.6"
msgid "yāva brahmalokāpi kāyena vasaṃ vattentan’ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="8"></a><a class="wp" id="wp5"></a>
msgctxt "dn11:11.1"
msgid "Tamenaṃ so assaddho appasanno taṃ saddhaṃ pasannaṃ evaṃ vadeyya:"
msgstr "But the one lacking faith and confidence would say to them:"

msgctxt "dn11:11.2"
msgid "‘atthi kho, bho, gandhārī nāma vijjā."
msgstr "‘There’s a spell named Gandhārī."

msgctxt "dn11:11.3"
msgid "Tāya so bhikkhu anekavihitaṃ iddhividhaṃ paccanubhoti—"
msgstr "Using that a mendicant can perform such superhuman feats.’"

msgctxt "dn11:11.4"
msgid "ekopi hutvā bahudhā hoti, bahudhāpi hutvā eko hoti …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn11:11.5"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn11:11.6"
msgid "yāva brahmalokāpi kāyena vasaṃ vattetī’ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="9"></a>
msgctxt "dn11:12.1"
msgid ""
"Taṃ kiṃ maññasi, kevaṭṭa, api nu so assaddho appasanno taṃ saddhaṃ pasannaṃ "
"evaṃ vadeyyā”ti?"
msgstr ""
"What do you think, Kevaddha? Wouldn’t someone lacking faith speak like that?”"

msgctxt "dn11:12.2"
msgid "“Vadeyya, bhante”ti."
msgstr "“They would, sir.”"

msgctxt "dn11:12.3"
msgid ""
"“Imaṃ kho ahaṃ, kevaṭṭa, iddhipāṭihāriye ādīnavaṃ sampassamāno "
"iddhipāṭihāriyena aṭṭīyāmi harāyāmi jigucchāmi."
msgstr ""
"“Seeing this drawback in psychic powers, I’m horrified, repelled, and "
"disgusted by demonstrations of psychic power."

#. </p><h2>
msgctxt "dn11:13.1"
msgid "2. Ādesanāpāṭihāriya"
msgstr "The Demonstration of Revealing"

#. </h2><p><a class="sc" id="10"></a><a class="wp" id="wp6"></a>
msgctxt "dn11:14.1"
msgid "Katamañca, kevaṭṭa, ādesanāpāṭihāriyaṃ?"
msgstr "And what is the demonstration of revealing?"

msgctxt "dn11:14.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, kevaṭṭa, bhikkhu parasattānaṃ parapuggalānaṃ cittampi ādisati, "
"cetasikampi ādisati, vitakkitampi ādisati, vicāritampi ādisati:"
msgstr ""
"In one case, someone reveals the mind, mentality, thoughts, and reflections "
"of other beings and individuals:"

msgctxt "dn11:14.3"
msgid "‘evampi te mano, itthampi te mano, itipi te cittan’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘This is what you’re thinking, such is your thought, and thus is your state "
"of mind.’ "

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="11"></a><a class="pts" id="pts1.214"></a>
msgctxt "dn11:15.1"
msgid ""
"Tamenaṃ aññataro saddho pasanno passati taṃ bhikkhuṃ parasattānaṃ "
"parapuggalānaṃ cittampi ādisantaṃ, cetasikampi ādisantaṃ, vitakkitampi "
"ādisantaṃ, vicāritampi ādisantaṃ:"
msgstr ""
"Then someone with faith and confidence sees that mendicant revealing other "
"person’s thoughts."

msgctxt "dn11:15.2"
msgid "‘evampi te mano, itthampi te mano, itipi te cittan’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn11:15.3"
msgid "Tamenaṃ so saddho pasanno aññatarassa assaddhassa appasannassa āroceti:"
msgstr "They tell someone else who lacks faith and confidence:"

msgctxt "dn11:15.4"
msgid ""
"‘acchariyaṃ vata bho, abbhutaṃ vata bho, samaṇassa mahiddhikatā "
"mahānubhāvatā."
msgstr ""
"‘It’s incredible, it’s amazing! The ascetic has such psychic power and might!"

msgctxt "dn11:15.5"
msgid ""
"Amāhaṃ bhikkhuṃ addasaṃ parasattānaṃ parapuggalānaṃ cittampi ādisantaṃ, "
"cetasikampi ādisantaṃ, vitakkitampi ādisantaṃ, vicāritampi ādisantaṃ:"
msgstr "I saw him myself, revealing the thoughts of another person!’"

msgctxt "dn11:15.6"
msgid "“evampi te mano, itthampi te mano, itipi te cittan”’ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="12"></a><a class="wp" id="wp7"></a>
msgctxt "dn11:16.1"
msgid "Tamenaṃ so assaddho appasanno taṃ saddhaṃ pasannaṃ evaṃ vadeyya:"
msgstr "But the one lacking faith and confidence would say to them:"

msgctxt "dn11:16.2"
msgid "‘atthi kho, bho, maṇikā nāma vijjā;"
msgstr "‘There’s a spell named Māṇikā."

msgctxt "dn11:16.3"
msgid ""
"tāya so bhikkhu parasattānaṃ parapuggalānaṃ cittampi ādisati, cetasikampi "
"ādisati, vitakkitampi ādisati, vicāritampi ādisati:"
msgstr "Using that a mendicant can reveal another person’s thoughts.’"

msgctxt "dn11:16.4"
msgid "“evampi te mano, itthampi te mano, itipi te cittan”’ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="13"></a>
msgctxt "dn11:17.1"
msgid ""
"Taṃ kiṃ maññasi, kevaṭṭa, api nu so assaddho appasanno taṃ saddhaṃ pasannaṃ "
"evaṃ vadeyyā”ti?"
msgstr ""
"What do you think, Kevaddha? Wouldn’t someone lacking faith speak like that?”"

msgctxt "dn11:17.2"
msgid "“Vadeyya, bhante”ti."
msgstr "“They would, sir.”"

msgctxt "dn11:17.3"
msgid ""
"“Imaṃ kho ahaṃ, kevaṭṭa, ādesanāpāṭihāriye ādīnavaṃ sampassamāno "
"ādesanāpāṭihāriyena aṭṭīyāmi harāyāmi jigucchāmi."
msgstr ""
"“Seeing this drawback in psychic powers, I’m horrified, repelled, and "
"disgusted by demonstrations of psychic power."

#. </p><h2>
msgctxt "dn11:18.1"
msgid "3. Anusāsanīpāṭihāriya"
msgstr "A Demonstration of Instruction"

#. </h2><p><a class="sc" id="14"></a><a class="wp" id="wp8"></a>
msgctxt "dn11:19.1"
msgid "Katamañca, kevaṭṭa, anusāsanīpāṭihāriyaṃ?"
msgstr "And what is a demonstration of instruction? "

msgctxt "dn11:19.2"
msgid "Idha, kevaṭṭa, bhikkhu evamanusāsati:"
msgstr "It’s when a mendicant instructs others like this:"

msgctxt "dn11:19.3"
msgid ""
"‘evaṃ vitakketha, mā evaṃ vitakkayittha, evaṃ manasikarotha, mā evaṃ "
"manasākattha, idaṃ pajahatha, idaṃ upasampajja viharathā’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘Think like this, not like that. Focus your mind like this, not like that. "
"Give up this, and live having achieved that.’"

msgctxt "dn11:19.4"
msgid "Idaṃ vuccati, kevaṭṭa, anusāsanīpāṭihāriyaṃ."
msgstr "This is called a demonstration of instruction."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="15"></a><a class="wp" id="wp9-66"></a><a
#. class="pts" id="pts1.215"></a>
msgctxt "dn11:20.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, kevaṭṭa, idha tathāgato loke uppajjati arahaṃ sammāsambuddho …"
msgstr "Furthermore, a Realized One arises in the world …"

msgctxt "dn11:20.2"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn11:20.3"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, kevaṭṭa, bhikkhu sīlasampanno hoti …"
msgstr "That’s how a mendicant is accomplished in ethics. …"

msgctxt "dn11:20.4"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn11:20.5"
msgid "paṭhamaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja viharati."
msgstr "They enter and remain in the first absorption …"

msgctxt "dn11:20.6"
msgid "Idampi vuccati, kevaṭṭa, anusāsanīpāṭihāriyaṃ …"
msgstr "This is called a demonstration of instruction."

msgctxt "dn11:20.7"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn11:20.8"
msgid "dutiyaṃ jhānaṃ …"
msgstr "They enter and remain in the second absorption …"

msgctxt "dn11:20.9"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn11:20.10"
msgid "tatiyaṃ jhānaṃ …"
msgstr "third absorption …"

msgctxt "dn11:20.11"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn11:20.12"
msgid "catutthaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja viharati."
msgstr "fourth absorption."

msgctxt "dn11:20.13"
msgid "Idampi vuccati, kevaṭṭa, anusāsanīpāṭihāriyaṃ …"
msgstr "This too is called a demonstration of instruction."

msgctxt "dn11:20.14"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn11:20.15"
msgid "ñāṇadassanāya cittaṃ abhinīharati abhininnāmeti …"
msgstr "They extend and project the mind toward knowledge and vision …"

msgctxt "dn11:20.16"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn11:20.17"
msgid "idampi vuccati, kevaṭṭa, anusāsanīpāṭihāriyaṃ …"
msgstr "This too is called a demonstration of instruction."

msgctxt "dn11:20.18"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn11:20.19"
msgid "nāparaṃ itthattāyāti pajānāti …"
msgstr "They understand: ‘… there is no return to any state of existence.’"

msgctxt "dn11:20.20"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn11:20.21"
msgid "idampi vuccati, kevaṭṭa, anusāsanīpāṭihāriyaṃ."
msgstr "This too is called a demonstration of instruction."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="16"></a><a class="wp" id="wp67"></a>
msgctxt "dn11:21.1"
msgid ""
"Imāni kho, kevaṭṭa, tīṇi pāṭihāriyāni mayā sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā "
"paveditāni."
msgstr ""
"These, Kevaddha, are three kinds of demonstration, which I declare having "
"realized them with my own insight."

#. </p><h2>
msgctxt "dn11:22.1"
msgid "4. Bhūtanirodhesakabhikkhuvatthu"
msgstr "On the Mendicant In Search of the Cessation of Being"

#. </h2><p><a class="sc" id="17"></a>
msgctxt "dn11:23.1"
msgid ""
"Bhūtapubbaṃ, kevaṭṭa, imasmiññeva bhikkhusaṅghe aññatarassa bhikkhuno evaṃ "
"cetaso parivitakko udapādi:"
msgstr ""
"Once it so happened, Kevaddha, that a mendicant in this very Saṅgha had the "
"following thought:"

msgctxt "dn11:23.2"
msgid ""
"‘kattha nu kho ime cattāro mahābhūtā aparisesā nirujjhanti, seyyathidaṃ—"
msgstr ""
"‘Where do these four primary elements cease without anything left over, "
"namely,"

msgctxt "dn11:23.3"
msgid "pathavīdhātu āpodhātu tejodhātu vāyodhātū’ti?"
